3. cs.SY (Systems and Control) - The paper deals with the problem of controlling multiple robots in a decentralized manner, which is a topic of interest in systems and control. 
4. cs.MA (Multi-Agent Systems) - The paper deals with multiple robots and their interactions, which is a topic of interest in multi-agent systems. 
5. cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) - The paper proposes a decentralized path planning algorithm, which involves designing efficient algorithms and can be considered as a topic of interest in data structures and algorithms.
